{"title_page": "Football at the Youth Olympic Games", "text_new": "{{Infobox Youth Olympic sport\n|sport = football\n|image = Football pictogram.svg\n|size = 150\n|boysevents = 1\n|girlsevents = 1\n}}\n'''[[Association football|Football]]''' was inducted at the [[Youth Olympic Games]] at the [[2010 Summer Youth Olympics|inaugural edition]] in 2010 for both boys and girls.\n\nFor the [[2018 Summer Youth Olympics|2018 edition]] in Buenos Aires, FIFA replaced football with [[futsal]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/about-fifa/news/y=2015/m=9/news=fifa-executive-vows-to-improve-governance-and-boost-female-participati-2696406.html|title=FIFA executive vows to improve governance and boost female participation in football|publisher=FIFA.com|date=25 September 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Football==\n===Boys===\n====Summaries====\n{| border=1 style=\"border-collapse:collapse; font-size:90%; text-align:center;\" cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0\n|- bgcolor=#C1D8FF\n!rowspan=2 width=5%|Year\n!rowspan=2 width=10%|Host\n!width=1% rowspan=100 bgcolor=ffffff|\n!colspan=3|Gold medal game\n!width=1% rowspan=100 bgcolor=ffffff|\n!colspan=3|Bronze medal game\n|- bgcolor=#EFEFEF\n!width=15%|Gold medalist\n!width=10%|Score\n!width=15%|Silver medalist\n!width=15%|Bronze medalist\n!width=10%|Score\n!width=15%|Fourth place\n|- bgcolor=#F5FAFF\n|2010<ref>[https://www.fifa.com/tournaments/archive/mensyoutholympic/singapore2010/index.html Boys' Youth Olympic Football Tournament Singapore 2010] [[FIFA.com]]</ref><br />''[[Football at the 2010 Summer Youth Olympics \u2013 Boys' tournament|Details]]''\n|{{flagicon|SIN}}<br>[[Singapore]]\n|'''{{fbu-big|15|BOL}}'''\n|'''5 \u2013 0'''\n|{{fbu-big|15|HAI}}\n|{{fbu-big|15|SIN}}\n|'''4 \u2013 1'''\n|{{fbu-big|15|MNE}}\n|- bgcolor=#D0E7FF\n|2014<br />''[[Football at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics \u2013 Boys' tournament|Details]]''\n|{{flagicon|CHN}}<br>[[Nanjing]]\n|'''{{fbu-big|15|PER}}'''\n|'''2 \u2013 1'''\n|{{fbu-big|15|KOR}}\n|{{fbu-big|15|ISL}}\n|'''4 